data.description: Unbeatable Combination Of Location And Affordability! Located just a mile from the heart of booming downtown Greer, this historic home is situated in a quiet residential area, yet literally within walking distance of both the Tryon Rec Center and also many dining and retail options. The home has a newer roof, newer HVAC, updated windows, gorgeous hardwood floors (including heart pine floors in the bedrooms), high baseboards, and is in move-in condition. Most buyers will want to eventually update the kitchen, and the home is priced to reflect this. The lot features a partially-fenced back yard and a 2-car carport. A previous owner enclosed a porch to make a third bedroom, though this room would also be perfect for a home office and/or a perfect spot to move the laundry out of the kitchen. This home is priced to sell at only $200,000!
